summary: An other design for anaos LayerBikini.
descriptionHtml:
An other design for anaos LayerBikini.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7736

Thanks to anano!

Installation UNP
After installation of LayerBikini for UNP, just drop the file in Data\\Textures\\Armor\\LayerBikini\\.

Installation CBBE:
After installation of ananos LayerBikini you find in the folder Data\\Textures\\Armor\\LayerBikini\\
some dds files with several bikini designs.
The actual used file by the mesh is \"BikiniEmerald.dds\". You have to replace this file by mine.
You can also examine the file femalebody_0.nif to find out, whitch dds is used.
author: Waldelf
